In SomeLibrary/ directory

emcmake cmake .
emmake make
emmake make install


In internal-project/ directory


Compile the wrapper code to LLVM bitcode
  emcc -c -std=c++11 -Ilibraries/SomeLibrary/install/include/SomeLibrary bind.cpp -o bind.bc


Convert the bitcode for both the library and the wrapper to JavaScript
  emcc --bind libraries/SomeLibrary/install/lib/libSomeLibrary.a bind.bc -o bind.js


** RJ's WebIDL equivalent **
/emscripten/tools/webidl_binder palmettoGallberry.idl glue
emcc wrapper.cpp -s WASM=0 -s EXPORTED_FUNCTIONS=["_malloc","_free"] --post-js glue.js -o behave.js


emcc EmScriptBinding.cpp my_glue_wrapper.cpp --post-js glue.js -o output.js
